				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 28 Jul 2020 04:18:59 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>RoyalJudas</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5622799</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Neat little concept. I do love SCPs created by people who just want to watch the world burn, and even more so SCPs that don't necessarily kill people. Also impressed with the lack of [REDACTED], makes for a nice read.</p> <p>My one criticism would be that the description and containment procedures aren't particularly well formatted. Too many full stops, not enough conjunctions.</p> <p>Overall a +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
