				<pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2019 15:58:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>aismallard</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4598089</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It's an interesting idea, and with further development could become something particularly good. However, as it is now, it has a few formatting and tonal issues that detract from it. The pacing is a bit slow, though you could rather easily improve that in my opinion by cutting lines that don't serve much of a purpose. Finally, is the recipe in the article? You said it's stored in an infohazard containment locker.</p> <p>Overall, novote.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
